::Ursa Major::

*raises her paw and taps on the door to the chamber*

"Hello?  Would someone kindly let me out please?"

*sits back and waits for someone to open the door.  She tries to remember 
what happened to her. She conducts and internal diagnostic.*

"Hmm, so far, so good.  Oh wait...Blast.  My memory circiuts were partially 
knocked out.  Oh geez, they will take some time to repair by themselves.  Oh 
man.  All I can remember is part of the crash to this planet. This is not 
good at all.  Of all the systems to have damaged. BLAST!"

*She hits her paw against the inside of the chamber as hard as she can.*

"Blast!"
